hadiths[43]{hadithnumber,text}:
3926,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid sey, wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' makatib par jab tak uski kitaabat (tey shuda raqam) ka eik dirham bhi baqi ho wo ghulam hai.''"
3927,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid sey, wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis ghulam ne so auqiya par kitaabat ka ehad kya ho, aur sab ada kar diya ho sirf das oqiye baqi reh gaey hun to wo ghulam hai, aur jis ghulam ne so Dinar par kitaabat ki ho aur sab ada kar chuka ho sirf das Dinar baqi hun to wo ghulam hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke) Amr bin Shuaib ka shagrid ( Abbas al-Jareeri, ye weham hai balke ye koi aur Shekh hai."
3928,"ummul-momenin Sayeda umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ham se farmaya : ''tum mein jab kisi ka ghulam makatib ho jaey aur uskey paas is qadr maal ho jo wo ada kar sakta ho to tumhen chahiye ke us se parda karo.''"
3929,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Hazrat Barira (Raziallahu anha) unke paas aai wo un se apney muahida kitaabat ke silsiley mein madad chahti thi aur apni kitaabat mein se kuch bhi ada nahin kar pai thi , to Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne us se kaha : apney ghar walon ke paas jao, agar wo pasand keren ke teri kitaabat mein ada kar dun aur tera wala mujhey hasil ho to main ye kerney ko tayyar hun. usney ja kar apney ghar walon ( malikon ( se baat ki to unhoney inkar kar diya aur kaha : agar wo ( Aaisha ( tujh par kharch karkey sawab lena chahen to ley lein , magar wala hamarey hi liye rahega . Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne ye baat Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se zikr ki, to aapney un se farmaya : ''usey kharid lo aur phir azad kar do . wala usi ka hota hai jo azad karey.'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khutba deney ke liye khadey huey aur farmaya : '' logon ko kya hua hai ke aisi aisi shartein kartey hain jo Allah ki kitab mein nahin hain jo koi aisi shart karey jo Allah ki kitab mein na ho to uska koi aetbar nahin, agar-che so shartein hi kyon na hun. Allah ki shart bar-haq aur mazboot hai.'' (yani uskey maa-siwa batil hain. ("
3930,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Barira (Raziallahu anha) apni kitaabat ke silsiley mein madad leney ke liye aai aur kaha : tehqiq maine apney ghar walon se no auqiya par makatibat kar li hai, her saal eik auqiya ada kya karun gi . chunanche aap meri kuch madad karen. Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : agar terey ghar waley ( Malik ( pasand keren to teri ye sari raqam mein yakmusht unhen dey deti hun aur tumhen azad kar deti hun aur tera wala merey liye hoga. to wo unke paas gaee . aur) Hisham ne ( Zohri ki riwayat ke manind bayan kya.  us riwayat mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke farman ke aakhir mein ye izafa hai.'' logon ko kya hua hai? eik kehta hai ke aey falan ! tum azad kar do aur wala mera raha , halanke wala usi ka hota hai jo azad karey.''"
3931,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai ke Juweriya bint Haris bin mustaliq Hazrat Sabit bin Qais bin shamas (Raziallahu anhu) , ya unke chacha zaad ke hissey mein aai. chunanche Juweriya ne apney baarey mein makatibat kar li . ye bahut khoobsurat khatoon thi aur her aankh ko bhali lagti thi. Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aai ke apni makatibat ke silsiley mein aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kuch madad ley . jab ye darwazey par khadi hui aur maine usko dekha to mujhey uska khada hona pasand na aaya . main jaan gaee ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bhi usi tarah dekhengey jaisey ke maine dekha hai. (yani wo bahut khoobsurat hai. ( usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main Haris ki beti Juweriya hun, mera maamla aap se chhipa hua nahin hai) ke jangi qaidi hun aur londi banai gaee hun ( mein Sabit bin Qais bin shamaas ke hissey mein aai hun. maine un se apney baarey makatibat kar li hai. main aap ki khidmat mein hazir hui hun aur meri darkhast hai ke makatibat ke silsiley mein meri madad farmaeyn, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum us se behtar maamla pasand nahin karti ho ?'' usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! wo kya hai? aapney farmaya : ''main tumhari taraf se tumhari kitaabat ada kar deta hun aur tum se shaadi kar leta hun.'' usney kaha : main razamand hun. Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain : phir logon ne ye khabar suni ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Juweriya (Raziallahu anha) se shaadi kar li hai. chunanche un sab ne jo qaidi unke qabzey mein they sab chhod diye aur unko azad kar diya. wo kehney lagey ye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke susrali rishte daar hain. ham ne nahin dekha ke us se badh kar koi aur aurat apney khandan ke liye ziyada barkat wali Sabit hui ho. uski wajeh se qabeela bano mustaliq ke eik so gharaney azad kiye gaey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ye hadees daleel hai ke wali apna nikah khud kar sakta hai."
3932,Hazrat Safina (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Sayeda Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ka ghulam tha. chunanche unhoney kaha : main tumhen is shart par azad karti hun ke tum zindagi bhar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat kartey rahogey . maine kaha : aap agar mujh se ye shart na bhi keren to main jeetey ji Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se juda na hunga . chunanche unhoney mujhey azad kar diya aur mujh se ye shart kar li .
3933,Janab abu-Maleeh ( Aamir ( apney walid ( Usama bin Umair ( se riwayat kartey hain ke eik shakhs ne eik ghulam ka apna hissey azad kar diya. phir ye baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko batai to aapney farmaya : ''Allah ka koi shareek nahin .'' ibn kaseer ne apni riwayat mein mazeed kaha : phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski azadi ko durust qarar diya.
3934,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik shakhs ne eik ghulam ka apna hissey azad kar diya, ( jabkey ghulam do afrad mein mushtarak tha ( to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski azadi ko durust qarar detey huey us azad kerney waley par baqiya ki qeemat ka tawaan bhi dal diya (taake wo kamil taur par azad ho jaey .)"
3935,"Janab Qatada apni sanad se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : '' jisney aisey ghulam ko azad kar diya ho jo ke uskey aur doosrey ke beech mushtarak ho, to us ( azad kerney waley ( par lazim hai ke usko khulaasi dilaaey .'' aur ye ibn suwed ke lafz hain."
3936,"Janab Qatada ne apni sanad se riwayat kya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney kisi ghulam ka apna hissey azad kar diya ho to us ( ghulam ( ko usi ke maal se azad kya jaeyga , agar uskey paas maal ho.'' ibn Musanna ne is sanad mein) Qatada ke Shekh ( nazar bin Anas ka naam nahin liya . aur ye alfaz ibn Suwed ke hain."
3937,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney apney mamlook ka koi hissey azad kar diya ho to us par lazim hai ke usey purey ko azad karey, agar uskey paas maal ho. warna ghulam se mehnat karaai jaey jo us par ziyada sakht aur shaaq na ho.''"
3938,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis kisi ne ( mushtarak ( ghulam mein se apna hissey azad kar diya ho to us ghulam ki azadi us ( azad kerney waley (ke maal se hogi b-sharte-ke uskey paas maal ho, agar uskey paas maal na ho to ghulam ki munasib qeemat lagai jaey, phir us se apney Malik ke liye qeemat ke mutabiq mehnat karaai jaey jo ziyada sakht aur bhari na ho. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : (Nasar bin Ali aur Ali bin Abdullah ( dono ki riwayat mein hai : (فاستسعي غير مشقوق عليه)  jabke mazkura baala alfaz Ali bin Abdullah ke hain (ke un mein (قوم العبد قيمة عدل ) ka bhi bayan hai. ("
3939,"Muhammad bin Bishr ne bayan kya, kaha : hamen Yahya aur ibne-abu-Adi ne Saeed bin abi Aruba se bayan kya, unhoney apni sanad se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : usey rooh bin Ubada ne pasand Saeed bin abu-Arooba riwayat kya, magar us mein mehnat karaney ka zikr nahin. isi tarah Jarir bin Hazim aur Musa bin khalaf dono ne Qatada se Yazid bin Zareeaa ki sanad sey is hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kya aur un dono ne mehnat karaney ka zikr kya hai."
3940,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney kisi ( mushtarak ( mamlook mein se apna hissey azad kar diya ho to us ( azad kerney waley ( par ghulam ki Aadilana qeemat lagai jaey aur wo apney shareekon ke hissey unhen ada kar dey aur uski taraf se ghulam ko azad kya jaey. warna us se jo azad ho gaya , so ho gaya .''"
3941,Janab Naafe ne b-waasta Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kya. Ayub kehtey hain ke Janab Naafe kabhi to (فقد عتق منه ما عتق) ke lafz zikr kartey aur kabhi na kartey.
3942,"Ayub ne Naafe sey, unhoney ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye hadees riwayat ki . Ayub ne kaha : mujhey nahin maloom ke hadees mein ye jumla (وإلا عتق منه ما عتق) nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka farmaya hua hai ya Naafe ki taraf se hai."
3943,"Naafe Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney apney mamlook ka hissa azad kar diya ho to us par lazim hai ke usey purey ko azad karey agar uskey paas uski qeemat ke b-qadr maal ho, agar uskey paas maal na ho to uska wohi hissey azad hua ( jo kya gaya .'' ("
3944,Janab Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se Ibrahim bin Musa ki) mazkura baala ( riwayat ke ham-maani riwayat kya.
3945,"Janab Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura riwayat Malik ( 3940 (ke ham-maani bayan kya. magar us mein (وإلا فقد عتق منه ما عتق) ka zikr nahin. uski hadees ( وأعتق عليه العبد ( par mukammal hui hai jo usi ke ham-maani hai."
3946,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney kisi mushtarak ghulam mein se apna hissey azad kar diya to uska baqi hissey bhi uskey maal se azad kya jaeyga jabkey uskey paas ghulam ki qeemat ke b-qadr maal mojud ho.''"
3947,"Janab Salim apney walid ( Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ( se riwayat kartey hain, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke ''jab koi ghulam do aadmiyon mein mushtarak ho aur un mein se eik apna hissey azad kar dey to agar wo sahibe-wusat ho to uski taraf se ghulam ki qeemat laga kar usey azad kar diya jaey, qeemat laganey mein kami ki jaey na ziyadti.''"
3948,"ibne-Tlib (Milqaam ( apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke eik shakhs ne ( mushtarak ( mamlook mein se apna hissey azad kar diya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey baqi ka zaamin aur zimmedar nahin banaya tha. Imam Ahmed (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke raawi ( ibne-Tlib) '' taa '' ke sath hai. aur Shoba (Rahimahullah) qadrey totle they, taa '' ( do nuqtey waley ( ko '' ثا '' ( teen nuqtey waley ( se numaya na kar saktey they."
3949,"Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya jaisey ke Hammad ka khayal hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo koi apney mehram rishtedaar ka Malik bin gaya ho to wo azad hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke Muhammad bin Bakr barsaai ne b-waasta Hammad bin Salma , Qatada sey, aur Aasim ne b-waasta Hasan Basri , Samra (Raziallahu anhu) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura hadees ke misl riwayat kya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : is hadees ko sirf Hammad bin Salma ne ( marfoo ya muttasil ( bayan kya hai aur us mein usey shak bhi hai."
3950,Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : jo apney kisi qaribi mehram rishtedaar ka Malik bin jaey to wo azad hai.
3951,Janab Hasan (Basri) (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : jo koi apney kisi qaribi mehram rishtedaar ka Malik bin jaey to wo azad hai.
3952,"Janab Qatada ne Jabir bin Zaid aur Hasan ( Basri) se usi ke misl bayan kya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne farmaya ke Saeed , Hammad ki nisbat zyada hifz waley hain."
3953,"Salama binte-Maaqil bayan karti hain aur ye bano khaarija Qais eilaan ki khatoon thin, kehti hain ke jahiliyat ke dinon mein mera chacha mujhey lekar aaya aur Hubaab bin Amr ke haath bech diya jo abu Yusr bin Amr ka bhai tha, to maine uskey bete Abdur-Rehman bin Hubab ko janm diya. phir wo (hubab) faut ho gaya to uski biwi ne kaha : Allah ki qasam ! ab tujhey Hubab ke qarzey mein bech diya jaeyga, to main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool! main bano khaarija Qais eilaan ki khatoon hun. jahiliyat key dinon mein mera chacha mujhey Madiney laya tha aur Hubab bin Amr, jo ke abu-Yusr bin Amr ka bhai hai, ke haath farokht kar diya tha. maine uskey bete Abdur-Rehman bin Hubab ko janm diya hai. aur ab uski biwi keh rahi hai Allah ki qasam ! tujhey us (Hubab) ke qarzey ki adaegi mein farokht kar diya jaeyga , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne daryaft farmaya : '' Hubab ka wali aur waris kon hai?'' bataya gaya ke uska bhai abu-Yusr bin Amr hai. to aapney usko bula bheja aur farmaya : '' usey aazad kar do aur jab tumhen maloom ho ke merey paas ghulam aaye hain to merey paas aana main tumhen uska badla de-dunga .'' Salama kehti hain ke phir unhoney mujhey azad kar diya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas ghulam aaye to aapney unko merey iwaz eik ghulam inayat farma diya."
3954,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kya ke ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke daur mein umme-walad laundiyon ko farokht kya tha, phir jab Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka daur aaya to unhoney hamen mana kar diya, to ham ruk gaey ."
3955,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne riwayat kya ke eik shakhs ne apney ghulam ke baarey mein keh diya ke wo uski wafat ke baad azad hoga, jabke uskey paas us ghulam ke siwa koi aur maal na tha, chunanche us ghulam ke baarey mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hukm diya to usey saat so ya no so mein farokht kya gaya."
3956,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne ye hadees bayan ki aur mazeed kaha . . . yani Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' to uski qeemat ka ziyada haqdaar (aur mohtaj ( hai, jabkey Allah azz-w-jall usko azad kiye janey se be parwa hai.'' ( usey koi ehtiyaaj nahin .)"
3957,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Abu-Mazkoor naami eik Ansari ne apney ghulam ke baarey mein keh diya ke meri maut ke baad wo azad hoga. . . us ghulam ka naam Yaqoob tha. . . aur us Ansari ka uskey siwa koi aur maal na tha. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us ghulam ko bulwaaya aur farmaya : ''isey kon khareedta hai? '' to Janab Nuem bin Abdullah bin nahaam ne usko aath so dirham mein kharid liya , chunanche aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye raqam Abu-Mazkoor ke hawaley ki aur farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi zaruratmand ho to chahiye ke (kharch kerney ki) apney se ibtida (shuruat) karey, agar kuch bach jaey to apney ayaal par kharch karey, agar un se bach rahey to apney qurbat daaron par kharch karey.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke alfaz (على ذي قرابته) they ya : (على ذي رحمه) aur agar bach rahey to idhar-udhar kharch kar dey .''"
3958,Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke eik shakhs ne apni wafat ke waqt apney chhe ghulam azad kar diye . us shakhs ke paas unke siwa koi aur maal na tha. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jab ye khabar mili to aapney usey badi sakht baat farmaai. phir un ghulamon ko bulwaaya aur unhen teen hisson mein taqseem kya. phir unmein qura andazi karkey do ko azad kar diya aur chaar ko ghulam hi rehney diya.
3959,Janab abu-Qulaba ne apni sanad se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kya. magar us mein ye jumla nahin hai : '' aapney usey badi sakht baat farmaai.''
3960,Janab Abu-Zaid se riwayat hai ke eik Ansari ne (apni maut ke waqt apney ghulam azad kar diye) mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kya aur kaha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar main uskey dafn kiye janey se pehley hazir hota to wo musalmanon ke qabristan mein dafn na kya jata.''
3961,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik shakhs ne apni maut ke waqt chhe ghulam azad kar diye jabke uska unke siwa koi aur maal na tha, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jab ye khabar pahunchi to aapney un ghulamon mein qura andazi karkey do ko azad kar diya aur chaar ko ghulam rakha ."
3962,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney ghulam azad kya ho aur uskey paas maal bhi ho to ghulam ka maal ghulam hi ka rahega siwaey iske ke Malik ne uski shart kar li ho (ke maal usey nahin diya jaeyga.'' (
3963,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''zina karnewala teeno mein se sab se bura hai.'' aur Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main eik kudra Allah ki raah mein de-dun wo us se behtar hai ke kisi zina zadey ko azad karun.
3964,"Ghareef bin Dailmi kehtey hain ke ham Hazrat Waasila bin Isqaa' (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur un se kaha : hamen hadees bayan keejiye jis mein koi kami beshi na ho, to wo ghussey ho gaey aur kehney lagey : bila-shuba tum mein kaee aisey hain jo Quran ki qirat kartey hain aur us mein kami beshi kar jatey hain, halanke Quran uskey apney ghar mein latka hua hota hai? ham ne kaha : hamara maqsad hai ke aisi hadees bayan farmaeyn jo aapney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suni ho. unhoney kaha : ham apney eik aadmi ke silsiley mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas hazir huey jo qatl ki wajeh se jahannam ka mustahiq ho chuka tha, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''uski taraf se ghulam azad kar do, Shan Wala Allah uskey har-har uzu (ang) ke badley uska eik-eik uzu aag se azad farma dega.''"
3965,"Janab Abu Najih Salma ( Amr bin Abasa (Raziallahu anhu)) bayan kartey hain ke ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath mein taaif ke mehal ka muhaasra kiya. Muaz (bin Hisham) kehtey hain ke maine apney walid se suna, wo kehtey they ke . . . eik qiley ka muhaasra kiya. . . aur mafhoom sab ka eik hai. Abu Najih ne kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ''jisney Allah ki raah mein teer chalaya uskey liye eik darja hai.'' aur puri hadees bayan ki. aur maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ''jis musalman ne kisi musalman ko azad kiya tu Allah taala uski eik eik haddi ko us azad karda ki eik eik haddi ke badley jahannam se tahaffuz aur bachao ka zarieaa bana dega. aur jis aurat ne kisi musalman aurat ko azad kiya to yaqinan Allah taala uski eik eik haddi ko uski azad karda ki eik eik haddi ke badley jahannam se tahaffuz aur bachao ka zarieaa bana dega.''"
3966,"Janab Shurehbil bin Samat kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Amr bin Abasa (Raziallahu anhu) se arz kiya ke hamein koi aisi hadees sunaeyn jo aapney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suni ho, to unhoney bayan kiya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna, aap farmatey they : ''jisney kisi musalman gardan ko azad kiya to wo uskey liye aag se bachao ke liye fidya hogi.''"
3967,"Janab Shurehbil bin Samat kehtey hain ke maine Kab bin Murra ya Murra bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke hamein koi aisi hadees sunaeyn jo aapney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suni ho to unhoney mazkura baala hadees Muaz bin Hisham ( 3965 (ke ham-maani bayan ki . . . aur mazeed kaha : ''jis shakhs ne do musalman aurton ko azad kiya wo uskey liye jahannam se azadi ka baais (wajah) hongi. unki har do haddiyon ko uski eik haddi ka iwaz (badal) bana diya jaeyga. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Salim ne Shurehbil se nahin suna, Shurehbil ki wafat siffieen mein hui thi."
3968,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs maut ke waqt azad karta hai uski misal us shakhs ki si hai jo pet bhar janey ke baad hadiya dey.''"
